---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout 
  title="Terms of Service | Claim Guardians" 
  description="Terms of Service for using the Claim Guardians website and services."
>
  <section class="section-white pt-32 pb-24">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6">
      <span class="eyebrow" style="color:#00808C;">Legal Agreement</span>
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-black text-[#082142] mb-12">Terms of Service</h1>
      
      <div class="prose prose-slate prose-lg lg:prose-xl font-medium text-slate-600 leading-relaxed space-y-8">
        <p><strong>Last Updated: March 19, 2026</strong></p>
        
        <p>By accessing or using the Claim Guardians LLC website (the "Site"), you agree to be bound by these Terms of Service. If you do not agree to these terms, please do not use the Site.</p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-black text-[#082142] pt-4">1. Use of the Site</h2>
        <p>The content on this Site is for informational purposes only and does not constitute legal or professional advice. Use of this Site does not create a public adjuster-client relationship until a formal contract is signed.</p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-black text-[#082142] pt-4">2. Intellectual Property</h2>
        <p>All content, logos, and designs on this Site are the property of Claim Guardians LLC and are protected by copyright and intellectual property laws. You may not reproduce or distribute any content without our prior written consent.</p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-black text-[#082142] pt-4">3. Limitation of Liability</h2>
        <p>Claim Guardians LLC is not liable for any direct or indirect damages arising from your use of the Site. We provide the Site "as is" without any warranties of any kind.</p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-black text-[#082142] pt-4">4. Governing Law</h2>
        <p>These terms are governed by the laws of the State of Florida. Any disputes arising from these terms will be resolved in the state or federal courts located in Florida.</p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-black text-[#082142] pt-4">5. Changes to Terms</h2>
        <p>We reserve the right to modify these Terms of Service at any time. Your continued use of the Site after changes are posted constitutes your acceptance of the new terms.</p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-black text-[#082142] pt-4">6. Contact</h2>
        <p>For any questions regarding these terms, please reach out to us at <span class="font-bold text-[#082142]">claims@claimguardians.com</span>.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
